summary: An island in the Iliac Bay.
descriptionHtml:
In the northeast of the Iliac bay is an island roughly three times the size of Whiterun. The natives lived a happy life, until the Orcs came from Orsinium to take the island; it's a useful vantage point.
---
There are no quests, and nor do I plan to add any. There is a boat in the Solitude docks to reach the island.
---
It's mainly a resource, do whatever you want with it.
author: Nutjob7
